title: Actress Anna Gunn on New Wall Street Film, 'Equity' (Audio)
itunes:title: Actress Anna Gunn on New Wall Street Film, 'Equity' (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Actress Anna Gunn, star of "Breaking Bad," will discuss her upcoming film, "EQUITY," the first female driven Wall Street film, opening July 29th.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
